,"text_app_in_store_mode_terminated_by_customer02":"Scanned products history will be deleted.","text_app_instore_mode_terminated":"In-store mode has ended.","text_app_pco_initial_hint":"Scan a product's QR code with the camera and the product will be added to your cart.","text_app_pco_instruction":"Scan a product's QR code with the camera in the UNIQLO app and the product will be added to your cart.","text_app_remove_all_scanned_item_confirmation":"Do you want to remove all scanned products?","text_app_remove_all_scanned_products":"Remove all products","text_app_remove_multiple_scanned_items":"In the case that there is more than one of the same item, they will all be deleted at once.","text_app_remove_scanned_item_confirmation":"text_app_remove_scanned_item_confirmation","text_app_successfully_scanned_item":"Successfully added","text_app_welcome_in_store_mode":"Welcome","text_persona_checkout_uqpay_register_required_description":"text_persona_checkout_uqpay_register_required_description","text_personal_checkout_failed_to_checkout":"text_personal_checkout_failed_to_checkout","text_unit_item_pirce":"Unit Price:","text_error_personal_checkout_general_message_01":"text_error_personal_checkout_general_message_01","text_error_personal_checkout_general_title":"text_error_personal_checkout_general_title","text_error_personal_checkout_service_unavailable_message_01":"text_error_personal_checkout_service_unavailable_message_01","text_error_personal_checkout_service_unavailable_title":"text_error_personal_checkout_service_unavailable_title","text_error_personal_checkout_shopping_bag_unavailable_message_01":"text_error_personal_checkout_shopping_bag_unavailable_message_01","text_error_personal_checkout_unavailable_item_in_cart_message_01":"text_error_personal_checkout_unavailable_item_in_cart_message_01","text_error_personal_checkout_unavailable_item_in_cart_title":"text_error_personal_checkout_unavailable_item_in_cart_title","text_store_name_place_holder":"text_store_name_place_holder","text_product_detail_solve_size_selection_message":"Get help with\\nfinding your size.","text_review_sampling_via_incentivized_campaign":"Reviewed via incentivized campaign","text_filter_clear_all_category":"Clear all categories","text_review_filter_height_weight_notees":"When filtering by height or weight, reviews with no height or weight input are not displayed.","text_review_most_helpful":"Most helpful","text_review_rating_high":"Rating (higher to lower)","text_review_rating_low":"Rating (lower to higher)","text_review_recently_posted":"Recently posted","text_rvw_gndr_001":"Male","text_rvw_gndr_002":"Female","text_rvw_gndr_003":"Other","text_rvw_gndr_004":"Decline to state","text_material_description":"This product contains at least 20% recycled material by product weight. Please refer to the Material composition and care instructions section above for the exact percentage of recycled material. Our aim is for 50% of all materials used in our products to be low-emission alternatives by 2030. The use of recycled materials is considered to contribute to mitigating climate change, promoting sustainable use of resources, and reducing waste.","text_material_description_note":"See the details section above for more information.","text_material_used":"Material:","text_processability":"Material","text_sewing_country_03":"Fabric dyeing:","text_store_inventory_status_by_nearest":"Nearby stores with available stock","text_store_inventory_status_by_nearest_out_of_stock":"Out of stock in nearby stores","text_traceability_description_note":"Fabric production information applies to products manufactured after Autumn/Winter 2024.","text_inventory_status_only_selected_store_stock_available_note":"This product is available at your favorite store! Shop it now with the \"ORDER & PICK\" button below.","text_product_detail_ask_question_via_chat":"Ask a question in chat","text_product_detail_check_size_wear_by_people_body_type_message":"Check the size worn by people with a similar body type to you.","text_product_detail_description_delivery_exchange_and_return_title":"Delivery / Exchange / Return","text_product_detail_description_details_title":"Details","text_product_detail_description_exchange_and_return_information":"Returns: Available only through our online returns portal. \nReturns accepted: Returns accepted within 30 days from the shipping date.\nReturn Shipping Cost: Rs. 50 applies for return shipments from the customer. Customers are responsible for return shipping fees unless the order received was incorrect.\nExchanges: Not available on online orders.\nFor more details about exchanges and returns, {link}.","text_product_detail_description_exchange_and_return_order_history_link":"View my purchase history","text_product_detail_description_exchange_and_return_policy_link":"conditions","text_product_detail_description_features_title":"Features","text_product_detail_description_materials_care_title":"Material / Care","text_product_detail_size_check_and_edit_recommend_image_capture_message":"See your recommended size","text_product_detail_size_check_dimension_and_product_message":"Check the dimensions of the product and compare the size with previously purchased products","text_product_detail_size_check_image_length_by_height_message":"Check the image of length by height","text_product_detail_styling_by_height":"Styling by Height","text_sustainability_information":"Production","text_bis_details_description01":"In case this item is discontinued OR does not come back in stock, you may not receive notification.","text_bis_details_description02":"You will receive a notification email when the item is back in stock.","text_bis_details_description03":"We will send you an email and app push notification after 8:00 AM on restock day.","text_bis_login_required":"Member Login is required to receive back in stock notifications.","text_bis_settings_completed":"Back in stock setting complete.","text_bis_settings_completed_description":"Back in stock notification setting completed.","text_bis_settings_completed_description02":"We will only send you a notification when an item is in stock.","text_bis_settings_completed_description03":"Notification will be sent if item is restocked in the next 120 days.","text_limited_offer_notes":"This product may continue to sell at a limited price or within a few days, even after the limited sales period shown. Also, prices may be reduced. Please be aware in advance.","text_limited_offer_notes_title":"Limited offer","text_select_color_coming_soon_date_late":"The selected color will be on sale in late {month}.","text_select_length_coming_soon_date_late":"The selected length will be on sale in late {month}.","text_select_size_coming_soon_date_late":"The selected size will be on sale in late {month}.","text_sewing_country":"Production:","text_sns_share_description":"You can share the page by clicking the icon.","text_tax_excluded_description":"The price does not include tax.","text_traceability":"*The information on material production locations applies to products manufactured after 24FW.","text_traceability_description":"We are continuously working to improve our verification of the production process in our supply chain both in-house and with third parties to have full understanding of the origins of raw materials, and the locations of the yarn spinning, fabric production, and garment sewing, knitting and assembly processes. This verification allows us to improve the quality of our clothing and also ensure safer manufacturing practices. We will continue to share information so customers can make informed choices about their clothing.","text_zero_review_product_description":"There are no reviews for this product. Be the first reviewer.","text_product_detail_contact_form":"text_product_detail_contact_form","text_dc_stock_may_allocate_note":"This product's delivery will be delayed from the original estimated delivery time by 2-3 days","text_product_detail_description_delivery_information":"Delivery Fee: Ship to Address is INR 250 for orders below INR 2999, free for INR 2999 and above; Click & Collect at UNIQLO stores is free. \nDelivery Timeline: Estimation time will appear at checkout after selecting preferred delivery method. \n{link} for more details.","text_product_detail_description_delivery_subtitle":"Delivery","text_select_length_coming_soon_date_early":"The selected length will be on sale in early {month}.","text_select_length_coming_soon_date_mid":"The selected length will be on sale in mid-{month}.","text_sewing_country_02":"Fabric knitting and weaving:","text_plus_tax":"+Tax","text_style_model_height":"cm","text_bis_app_push_notification_setting_on":"Please enable the UNIQLO app push notification setting to receive the message on the app.","text_bis_notification_available_subtitle":"Restock notification available","text_style_model_wearing_size":"Size:","text_no_items":"There are no items.","text_style_staff_customer_styling_title":"Looks from the global community","text_style_styling_date":"YYYY/MM/DD","text_style_styling_date_update":"Update","text_bis_notification_available_description_01":"You will receive a restock notification via the app or email after 8:00AM on the day the product is back in stock.","text_bis_notification_available_description_02":"In case this item is discontinued OR does not come back in stock, you may not receive notification.","text_inventory_status_only_selected_store_stock_available_description":"If the product is sold out online, it may be available in store.","text_bis_available_notes":"Notifications","text_bis_notification_or_selected_store_stock_available_subtitle":"Get back in stock notifications or check store availability","text_post_comments":"Submit","text_post_completion":"Thanks for your review","text_post_thankyou":"Please note that your review may take up to 48 hours to appear.","text_ph_alteration_length":"None","text_ph_alteration_type":"None","text_bis_available_notes01":"Notifications","text_bis_description01":"You will receive a notification email when item is back in stock.","text_bis_description02":"To purchase the item, please proceed to Checkout through the notification email.","text_error_pre_order_high_threshold_cart_product_message":"Please remove {no: of items} quantity(ies) from this product as it will take time to arrive at the warehouse.","text_error_pre_order_high_threshold_cart_product_message_equal_quantity":"Please remove this product as it will take time to arrive at the warehouse.","text_error_pre_order_high_threshold_cart_top_message":"The order contains items that will take longer to arrive. Please remove those items and try purchasing again.","text_select_color_coming_soon_date_early":"The selected color will be on sale in early {month}.","text_select_color_coming_soon_date_mid":"The selected color will be on sale in mid-{month}.","text_select_size_coming_soon_date_early":"The selected size will be on sale in early {month}.","text_select_size_coming_soon_date_mid":"The selected size will be on sale in mid-{month}.","text_error_failed_get_current_store":"Failed to get current store information","text_no_messages":"There are no messages.","text_error_gift_wrapping_unavailable_add_to_cart":"Please note: Gift wrapping is unavailable due to item quantity or the size too large. Please remove the option or edit your order.","text_error_gift_wrapping_unavailable_apply_gift_option":"Please note: Gift wrapping is unavailable due to item quantity or the size too large. Please remove the option or edit your order.","text_error_gift_wrapping_unavailable_cart":"Please note: Gift wrapping is unavailable due to item quantity or the size too large. Please remove the option or edit your order.","text_error_gift_wrapping_unavailable_place_order":"Please note: Gift wrapping is unavailable due to item quantity or the size too large. Please remove the option or edit your order.","text_length_guide_by_height":"Length Guide by Height","text_c