nce.","text_error_locker_pickup_inside_multiple_orders":"Multiple orders were found for the entered number. A UNIQLO team member will assist you shortly.","text_error_locker_pickup_inside_multiple_orders_description_01":"Apologies for the inconvenience. Please locate a UNIQLO team member for assistance.","text_error_locker_pickup_inside_order_not_found":"No orders available for collection","text_error_locker_pickup_inside_order_not_found_description_01":"Apologies for the inconvenience. Please locate a UNIQLO team member for assistance.","text_error_locker_pickup_inside_general_message":"System error","text_error_locker_pickup_inside_general_message_description_01":"Apologies for the inconvenience. Please locate a UNIQLO team member for assistance.","text_error_locker_pickup_outside_order_not_stored":"No orders available for collection","text_error_locker_pickup_outside_order_not_stored_description_01":"Apologies for the inconvenience. Please locate a UNIQLO team member for assistance.","text_error_locker_pickup_outside_order_not_found":"No orders available for collection","text_error_locker_pickup_outside_order_not_found_description_01":"Apologies for the inconvenience. Please locate a UNIQLO team member for assistance.","text_error_locker_pickup_outside_general_message":"System error","text_error_locker_pickup_outside_general_message_description_01":"Apologies for the inconvenience. Please locate a UNIQLO team member for assistance.","NSBluetoothAlwaysUsageDescription":"To pick up your order from the store locker, please allow Bluetooth access.","text_error_locker_pickup_common_title":"System error","text_error_locker_pickup_common_message_01":"Apologies for the inconvenience. Please locate a UNIQLO team member for assistance.","text_online_store_service_survey":"Online shopping service survey","text_test_ph_search_form":"Search by keyword","text_shipping_speed_option_same_day_delivery":"text_shipping_speed_option_same_day_delivery","text_shipping_speed_option_una