_description_07":"The refund will be processed once & only if the item passes our quality check.","text_return_form_notes_description_05":"To cancel return, please ask delivery partner to cancel this return request by sharing OTP with the delivery partner when the delivery partner contacts for the Return Pick-up.","text_return_form_notes_description_06":"Once return is raised it can't be self cancelled by the customer on Uniqlo App/Website. For more assistance please get in touch with our customer service team.","text_return_form_return_condition_17":"Only return & refund is allowed for items meetings our return policy.","text_return_form_return_condition_18":"Exchange is not allowed for items purchased online.","text_return_form_how_to_return_06":"Shipping Carrier will visit your location for the pickup of the items.","text_return_form_how_to_return_06_description_01":"The items will be picked up from your location within 1-3 business days once return is submitted on app/website. Return Tracking details will be shared on customer's registered contact number & email address.","text_order_history_delivery_status_track_button":"text_order_history_delivery_status_track_button","text_order_history_delivery_status_title":"text_order_history_delivery_status_title","text_shipping_speed_option_unavailable_description_12":"text_shipping_speed_option_unavailable_description_12","text_shipping_speed_option_unavailable_description_13":"text_shipping_speed_option_unavailable_description_13","text_gopay_qr_code_failed_display":"text_gopay_qr_code_failed_display","text_return_form_how_to_return_03_sub_description_02":"text_return_form_how_to_return_03_sub_description_02","text_return_form_end_of_step_1_message_description_01":"text_return_form_end_of_step_1_message_description_01","text_return_form_about_refund_description_08":"text_return_form_about_refund_description_08","text_return_form_return_condition_19":"text_return_form_return_condition_19","text_dpd":"DPD","text_mondial_