II submitted are complete, true, accurate, adequate and up-to-date.","text_invoice_agreement_description_02":"Please click “Agree” to continue requesting E-invoice.","text_invoice_request_completed":"Request completed","text_invoice_request_completed_description_01":"Your E-invoice request has been received and will be processed within 72 hours after receiving of goods. Please check your spam/ junk mail folder to make sure you don’t miss any email. For further assistance please reach out to our {link}.","text_invoice_cancel_confirmation":"Cancel confirmation","text_invoice_cancel_confirmation_description":"Do you want to cancel E-invoice request?","text_invoice_imark_description_01":"In conjunction of the e-invoicing Guidelines issued by the Inland Revenue Board of Malaysia (“IRBM”), Uniqlo (Malaysia) Sdn Bhd (“Uniqlo”) is required to collect information, which includes personal data/personal identifiable information i.e. name, NRIC/passport number, tax identification number, residential address, contact number, email (“PII”), from you to generate the e-Invoice (“Purpose”).  By providing the information and PII requested, you have acknowledged and consent to the collection, use and processing of your information and PII in accordance with the Personal Data Protection Act 2010 (“PDPA”). All of the information and PII submitted to Uniqlo will be treated as strictly private and confidential and be processed in accordance to Uniqlo Privacy Policy.","text_invoice_imark_description_02":"Uniqlo reserves the right to change or revise the Privacy Policy therefore you are advised to visit our website from time to time to check if there are any amendments made to this Privacy Policy.","text_invoice_imark_description_03":"By providing the necessary information and PII, you agree to receive and process e-Invoice electronically in compliance with the e-invoicing rules and regulations set forth by the government.","text_invoice_imark_description_04":"This e-Invoice is not a substitute for the receipts/invoices for your purchases from Uniqlo and cannot be used for any return and exchange.","text_payment_method_upi_description":"Select either UPI payment option or UPI ID.","text_upi_payment_option":"UPI payment option","text_upi_payment_option_upi_id":"UPI ID","text_upi_payment_option_upi_qr_code":"UPI QR","text_upi_payment_id_input_form_placeholder":"Please enter your UPI ID.","text_upi_payment_id_input_form_hint":"Eg: 1234567890@upi","text_upi_payment_place_order":"Press \"Place Order\" to proceed with the UPI payment method.","text_upi_payment_qr_code_title":"Payment with UPI QR code","text_upi_payment_qr_code_description":"Scan the QR code with any UPI compatible app to complete the payment. Please do NOT press the back button, close or refresh this window. QR will automatically expire in {countdownTimer} mins.","text_upi_payment_completed_description_01":"Thank you for purchasing. We have received your order. Please complete your payment on your selected app within 5 minutes.","text_thirty_days_lowest_price":"text_thirty_days_lowest_price","text_thirty_days_lowest_price_imark_title":"text_thirty_days_lowest_price_imark_title","text_thirty_days_lowest_price_imark_description_01":"text_thirty_days_lowest_price_imark_description_01","text_uk_thirty_days_lowest_price_imark_title":"text_uk_thirty_days_lowest_price_imark_title","text_thirty_days_lowest_price_imark_sub_title_01":"text_thirty_days_lowest_price_imark_sub_title_01","text_thirty_days_lowest_price_imark_description_02":"text_thirty_days_lowest_price_imark_description_02","text_thirty_days_lowest_price_imark_sub_title_02":"text_thirty_days_lowest_price_imark_sub_title_02","text_thirty_days_lowest_price_imark_description_03":"text_thirty_days_lowest_price_imark_description_03","text_thirty_days_lowest_price_imark_description_04":"text_thirty_days_lowest_price_imark_description_04","text_deliveree":"text_deliveree","text_nittsu":"text_nittsu","text_jne":"text_jne","text_tge":"text_tge",